      <title>道格·福特（Doug Ford</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/doug-ford-wins-third-majority-in-ontario-amid-trade-war-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道格·福特（Doug Ford）连续第三次选举领导安大略省，因为加拿大制造业心脏地带的选民选择了一个熟悉的面孔来引导美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易政策受到威胁的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/doug-ford-wins-third-majority-in-ontario-amid-trade-war-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:19:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在Zelenskiy上柔和的语气，但没有支持乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-softens-tone-on-zelenskiy-but-not-on-backing-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）总统于周五到达白宫，个人呼吁唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在急于与俄罗斯达成和平协议中不卖掉自己的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-softens-tone-on-zelenskiy-but-not-on-backing-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对习近平施加压力，最新威胁要提高关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布了对中国进口的额外关税，这增加了北京进一步报复的风险，以及世界上两个最大经济体之间紧张局势的螺旋螺旋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普所说，中国股票下跌，我们将征收更多的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-says-us-will-impose-more-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他将对亚洲国家的进口征收额外的10％税，这一发展增加了投资者对加剧贸易紧张局势的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-says-us-will-impose-more-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的最新关税震动有市场警报中国的回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-s-latest-tariff-jolt-has-markets-alert-for-china-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最新的关税威胁促使投资者淘汰中国的反应，而诸如新鲜刺激和宽松的货币政策之类的举动被认为是桌面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-s-latest-tariff-jolt-has-markets-alert-for-china-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:39:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚总统说，不久的将来会有更多内阁变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/colombian-president-says-more-cabinet-changes-are-coming-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）表示，他将在不久的将来对内阁进行更多更改。]]></description>
